Titolo: Escaped Chasm

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Escaped Chasm is a 2019 adventure game developed by Undertale artist Temmie Chang. It was released on her birthday on the independent video game site, Itch.io, as freeware and marks her debut as a video game developer. The game depicts themes of abandonment, depression, and surrealism.
The game is loosely based on Chang's short film, Dwellers of the Mountain's Forest, and is the first installment of her series, The Dwellers Universe.The game received praise from players for her video game debut and Fox's musical score. It has a 4.7 star rating with more than 850 reviews, making it the second highest rated RPG Maker game on itch.io behind Lonely Wolf Treat. An indirect sequel, Dweller's Empty Path (also known as Escaped Chasm 2), with Gameboy-style graphics, was released on July 10, 2020.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
